Contributing

The vtreat project is happy to examine good faith issues and pull requests here. Also please feel free to email the maintaining contributor: John Mount jmount@win-vector.com.

Please understand we can not accept any code without having full rights and license assigned to Win-Vector LLC.

Also we expect contributors to follow GitHub Community Guidelines.
